 I was trying to find the least-objectionable term to <br>
express my POV.  Every other way to express that concept<br>
seemed to carry a connotation and/or a denotation.<br>
I'm trying to express myself WITHOUT insulting you.<br>
Work with me, here.<br>
<br>
=======================================<br>
BTW, <br>
I object to someone's statement that if we didn't have<br>
tradition, we would have no Bible.<br>
God will accomplish His purposes DESPITE us if we won't<br>
work with Him.  Strictly speaking, He wants us but does not<br>
NEED us.<br>
<br>
<br>
Does anyone besides me think a brisk walk around the block<br>
might be a good idea around here?<br>
I think the engine's running a little hot....<br>
