This is a topic in itself.  Jeff is right, we have to define <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Scripture</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> in this verse.  The New Testament was not in existence when this was spoken, and, from what I understand, the Old Testament was still being defined.<br>
